            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">We're experiencing some technical difficulties.<br/>Our team has been notified and is working on the issue.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm mb-8 mx-auto max-w-md">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">What you can try:</h3>
            <ul class="text-left text-gray-600 space-y-2 mb-4">
                <li class="flex items-center">
                    <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2 text-green-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 4v5h.582m15.356 2A8.001 8.001 0 004.582 9m0 0H9m11 11v-5h-.581m0 0a8.003 8.003 0 01-15.357-2m15.357 2H15"/>
